Class DefaultErrorHandler

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ErrorHandler

    public class DefaultErrorHandler
extends CombineErrorHandler
    ErrorHandler implementation that is used by default in APF plugins.

    To replace ErrorHandlers in use call CombineErrorHandler.setErrorHandlers(ErrorHandler...).
